{"tid":2238461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死因無可疑        支那女墮樓死","createTime":"2020-10-11T07:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T07:17:08.000Z","uid":374134,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c6f672ac8fa2bd8ae7ee6d1c6dfed07265fa68","tid":2238461,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:02:11.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名就讀國小六年級的女童突然爬上社區頂樓，翻過圍牆後用手拉住鋼筋，整個人直接懸掛在半空；當時樓下不斷傳來撕心裂肺的叫喊聲，孩子似乎猶豫了一會，最後還是鬆開雙手，從26樓墜下慘死。事發後，有鄰居透露，女童疑因沒完成作業遭家長責罵，一時想不開才做出傻事。<br />\n《紅星新聞》報導，這起憾事發生在本月9日，家住廣西省平果市的小六女童當天放學回到家不久，突然出現在社區頂樓，並翻過女兒牆爬上雨遮，接著僅用雙手拽住邊緣的鋼筋，全身懸空吊掛在半空中；根據現場畫面，女童吊在空中時，樓下不斷傳出淒厲的哭喊聲，讓她躊躇了一會，無奈最後還是選擇放手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ep1Bcac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEp1Bcac.jpg&h=04540649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報導指出，事發大樓足足有26層高，因此女童重摔落地後，當場便失去生命跡象，送醫後仍回天乏術。針對案發原因，社區住戶透露，女孩疑似沒能在國慶連假期間完成老師交代的作業，家長接到師長電話後，氣得責備了孩子，最終才釀成憾事。<br />\n對此，平果市公安局表示，他們在案發後第一時間就趕到現場了解情況，但具體原因還在調查中，教育局方面也還沒有給出說法；教育局人員則稱，目前警方已召集學校和家長進行溝通、問話，具體原因還沒有定論，究竟是否因作業問題導致女童輕生，仍有待進一步查證。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201011/1828776.htm#ixzz6aXlWqXUh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201011%2F1828776.htm%23ixzz6aXlWqXUh&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlcIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=283d2c05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201011/1828776.htm#ixzz6aXlWqXUh</a>"},{"pid":"907d9cfef091253880b99c287ce92a25b55c4eef","tid":2238461,"uid":27946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"中國橫掂人多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbbf9aaade1be0a88f09d526e8f00bdd753902d1","tid":2238461,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"仲諗住有步兵既片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07dd83f350f6ab4854d4fd9c69a174cad61be44","tid":2238461,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"Push 大家一齊笑吓"},{"pid":"77678e63038b2190112f97ebd1d3331f3fabee91","tid":2238461,"uid":258960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>「孩子似乎猶豫了一會，最後還是鬆開雙手」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇黎都係頂唔緊，一心想重刷"},{"pid":"88556d49bc77166423a60793c77c0049f0b257a8","tid":2238461,"uid":374134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"求Gina冇人無辜  嗰個gif"},{"pid":"e58bd747e9fa79c3a9f6d697c22f0ff23540e295","tid":2238461,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77678e63038b2190112f97ebd1d3331f3fabee91","tid":2238461,"uid":258960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>「孩子似乎猶豫了一會，最後還是鬆開雙手」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇黎都係頂唔緊，一心想重刷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"人生最後幾秒"},{"pid":"1973a0b2fd26f227bc1e0adbff79aa0bf486d0b0","tid":2238461,"uid":327462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YORQ06V.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYORQ06V.gif&h=e02d4285&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fee85f768bbd77abe4d0d96e41aace2141f45e7a","tid":2238461,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T07:14:20.000Z